Subject: Re: [VB] Clutch

you can also usually go to any vw repair place that has any kind of junk
trannies laying around/torn apart, or even a junkyard and usually get a
used input shaft for nothing. the only important part really is the splines
and they are the same size for all air cooled models. plastic ones are
available also for about $2. 


